Google在[[Chrome_OS|Chrome OS]]中使用zram，它也成为了[[Android|Android]] 4.4设备的一个选项<ref name="chromestory">{{cite web |url=http://www.chromestory.com/2013/03/google-enabling-zram-for-chrome-os-by-default/ |title=Google is Enabling zram for Chrome OS By Default |accessdate=29 March 2013 |4= |last=Larabel |first=Michael |website=chromestory.com |date=28 March 2013 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130222943/http://www.chromestory.com/2013/03/google-enabling-zram-for-chrome-os-by-default/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>Google, [http://developer.android.com/about/versions/kitkat.html Android KitKat | Android Developers] {{Wayback|url=http://developer.android.com/about/versions/kitkat.html |date=20131031184317 }}</ref>。此外，[[Lubuntu|Lubuntu]]于13.10开始使用zram<ref>{{cite web |url=http://linuxvillage.org/en/2013/10/next-lubuntu-provided-with-zram-enabled/ |title=Next Lubuntu provided with zram enabled! – LinuxVillage (en) |website=linuxvillage.org |date=17 October 2013 |accessdate=10 November 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110202741/http://linuxvillage.org/en/2013/10/next-lubuntu-provided-with-zram-enabled/ |archivedate=2013年11月10日 }}</ref>。{{As of|2012|12}}，Ubuntu考虑为小内存的计算机默认启用zram<ref name="phoronix">{{cite web|url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTI0NjQ/|title=Ubuntu Linux Considers Greater Usage of zRAM|accessdate=30 October 2013|4=|last=Dinsan|first=Francis|date=8 December 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180830210228/https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTI0NjQ%2F|archive-date=2018-08-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

